data.description: ***UPDATE - Owner will be painting the home neutral colors or white on 2/27/21 & 2/28/21.*** Don't let this one go!  This home boasts just over 3,000 square feet with a total of 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths and 1 half bath.  The owner's bedroom is on the main level for convenience and has a huge walk in closet with attached bath with double vanity sinks. Laundry is also on the main level.  Enjoy a dinner party with friends and family and make use of the large dining room and kitchen.  The family room is spacious and the television mounted on the wall conveys!  Upstairs has two large bedrooms and a full bath.  Downstairs is where to be!  The basement has a bar custom made by the owner that is great for entertaining guests.  The television mounted to the wall in the basement also conveys!  There is plenty of space with a game room, family room, AND a bonus room with closet that could be used for an extra bedroom/den/office.  Basement has a separate entrance with walk-out.  Plenty of parking also with the attached two car garage, and drive way with turn around spot or can use as an extra parking space.  Rear yard is fenced with two gated entrances.  This home is located in the highly sought Hammonds Mill community.  Schedule your showing today!
